{
  "enabled": true,
  "name": "Feature Testing Review",
  "description": "Reviews recently modified code to identify what was built, what functionality should be tested by users, and generates a testing checklist with potential issues to watch for",
  "version": "1",
  "when": {
    "type": "userTriggered"
  },
  "then": {
    "type": "askAgent",
    "prompt": "Review the recently changed files and provide:\n\n1. **What Was Built**: Summarize the features/components that were added or modified\n2. **User Testing Checklist**: Create a clear, step-by-step testing plan for the user to follow, including:\n   - Specific actions to take\n   - Expected results\n   - Edge cases to test\n   - Different scenarios (happy path and error cases)\n3. **Potential Issues to Watch For**: List things that might need fixing based on the code review\n4. **Testing Notes**: Any special setup needed or important context for testing\n\nFormat this as a clear, actionable testing guide that a non-technical user can follow."
  }
}